{"tid":330742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打一路心思思想謀反？","createTime":"2017-07-21T13:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T00:52:44.000Z","uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ecc79caedad5c1a9544aa37c0e5d289e03b822","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:31:18.000Z","msg":"阿爸教落做男人要有野心 要有大志<br />\n係呢間公司做左幾年 <br />\n由細做起 做足人地200%嘅嘢<br />\n基本上而家坐到呢個位<br />\n所有流程 數 客方面 各個department嘅無論人同事<br />\n我都熟<br />\n客源人脈穩定，keep 住有大Job做<br />\n我好肯定講 我拉兩team人走 拉一半大客走<br />\n已經可以摧毀呢間公司<br />\n如果準備充足<br />\n應該半年至九個月可以回本 翻倍<br />\n但自立門戶風險亦相對好大 最壞情況係破產同呢行做過街老鼠<br />\n老老實實 搵到錢仆街我唔怕做<br />\n我呢排慢慢放緊風比熟我嘅下屬<br />\n想問下巴打有無相關經驗？"},{"pid":"8e4c8e37a32a14ff401a2b9abf39cbe8930cbc86","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"前排轉post 睇左份約<br />\n寫離職後半年不得以員工身份從事相關行業<br />\n問左律師 做老闆投資者係無抵觸"},{"pid":"7aa9a75e58b30a53ea7afe5eeab98a960d5419fb","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d22832a51bc7a5a76e509d077673f0e2a6b49f","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84ff87ed4064b68e09b20e5ff360bdf67d4fd9f","tid":330742,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"唔好睇得自己咁重啦巴打<br />\n<br />\n你係咁位高權重 咁有影響力 老細都賣你怕啦 要風得風要雨得雨<br />\n<br />\n好多人口講跟你走 好多客又話淨係跟你 實際上都係講講下咋"},{"pid":"a68bb9e39721265b4d1643cc365e21091f0c1993","tid":330742,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排轉post 睇左份約<br />\n寫離職後半年不得以員工身份從事相關行業<br />\n問左律師 做老闆投資者係無抵觸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你D同事咪唔做得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c77a35a7b9417038123bee10cb574346bb908f","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前排轉post 睇左份約<br />\n寫離職後半年不得以員工身份從事相關行業<br />\n問左律師 做老闆投資者係無抵觸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你D同事咪唔做得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以想睇下有無巴打有計？"},{"pid":"940050f858f6f4b9f2717d5299d83ca389add56e","tid":330742,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"多唔多自己老友先"},{"pid":"e11256bdc1fbdbbc52d73714bef09bb62228daea","tid":330742,"uid":81686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"自己做老細吧巴打<br />\n你有呢個諗法即係你內心根本就好想自立門戶<br />\n祝你成功"},{"pid":"7903fb1e501e01cccf18f01be787565b52507371","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好睇得自己咁重啦巴打<br />\n<br />\n你係咁位高權重 咁有影響力 老細都賣你怕啦 要風得風要雨得雨<br />\n<br />\n好多人口講跟你走 好多客又話淨係跟你 實際上都係講講下咋</blockquote><br />\n老老實實 事實我係係公司真係同老闆無咩分別 係有d doc要佢同我師父簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08c3efa51870b393c62bf67e6b17e515f2a3712","tid":330742,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"邊行"},{"pid":"d77a5a8d221f9edd481d40b554bf8464e7358dc8","tid":330742,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63635e3fec4ccea341ddfce879680e7cae450a44","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多唔多自己老友先</blockquote><br />\n對人好簡單嘅啫<br />\n一係對自己有好處<br />\n一係勢力大到你唔主動埋堆係你成為異類<br />\n令你想巴結多過想對抗<br />\n我偏好第二種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0498c0d56969fcc6b91864d17a1f96512031c3f4","tid":330742,"uid":74281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"信你一成雙目失明 信你兩成尻都變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e7bdf2023a1f8e579108c850dad425a367836a","tid":330742,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4caf9e54d541427b0799c83f2b8f2dce4df9fc3","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晒氣啦<br />\n<br />\n你連出糧既錢都搞唔掂啦<br />\n<br />\n何況好地地做咩要跟你走?<br />\n<br />\n仲有D客咪又係睇錢<br />\n<br />\n低過你宜家公司隨時打個和  高過D客咪又係唔搵你</blockquote><br />\n巴打，唔怕老實同你講<br />\n做我呢行，性質好似娛樂圈<br />\nsocial係重要，根本有好多好撚有錢既人<br />\n唔係睇你做唔做到野，係睇你既人脈對佢有無好處<br />\n基本上間間公司都係做類似嘅野，睇遠少少<br />\n幾時都係呀巴打，連帶關係勝於一切<br />\n如果只係針對價錢去做生意 執柒左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e4be5cd34a7371200b5672298e04856439616c","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>信你一成雙目失明 信你兩成尻都變形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋絕大部份老闆都係有家底<br />\n而唔係中途轉老闆</blockquote><br />\n咁你又啱，安於現況打份工都對我無影響嘅<br />\n係後生想博一博姐"},{"pid":"3c1ceee19dd508f0ad165492d7d10d4f51eb6b3e","tid":330742,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"以為講緊港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bee173f1e7ce8cae018c77833ad084dc24e7835","tid":330742,"uid":8721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"字裡行間睇唔透你係想自立門户 定係想摧毀你呢間公司<br />\n<br />\n四個字 飲水思源<br />\n<br />\n唔好純粹想証明自己有能力以去做，要搵錢仲有好多方法"},{"pid":"ece74b8e2eadbefe0b2474faea1fc1abd3574bd2","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:24:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>字裡行間睇唔透你係想自立門户 定係想摧毀你呢間公司<br />\n<br />\n四個字 飲水思源<br />\n<br />\n唔好純粹想証明自己有能力以去做，要搵錢仲有好多方法</blockquote><br />\n可以同時進行嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ebb8a91ccc3ff2e96dc0e2517df2f79fa0f16f","tid":330742,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"咪咁傻 <br />\n識幾個人都以為自己做起咗巴屎閉起老細飛腳<br />\n最後個朵臭哂 收埋皮"},{"pid":"f55de80861ae08cf10b42daff2213ebbaa41755b","tid":330742,"uid":89999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"你諗野咁簡單唔好做耇闆"},{"pid":"91f62c051d3b5e43dd89d8ff962560440718b64c","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T19:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪咁傻 <br />\n識幾個人都以為自己做起咗巴屎閉起老細飛腳<br />\n最後個朵臭哂 收埋皮</blockquote><br />\n都驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70eeeab7d8c0645c49ed15f1fd534f7c8035aeb","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T19:32:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你諗野咁簡單唔好做耇闆</blockquote><br />\n點解咁講？"},{"pid":"15d7687320c330eb0907f09b2b790a735d8df1ae","tid":330742,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T00:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}